## Hypothesis 

![:space 15]

### Violent Non-State Actors with ![:text_color steelblue](**higher levels of knowledge diversity**) (_those with more heterogeneous members_) will tactically ![:text_color steelblue](**innovate more often**) than organizations with lower levels of knowledge diverseity (_those with more homogeneous members_)

